{"tid":128353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]江西女鐵鏈勒頸掛屍河邊　警判斷為自縊","createTime":"2017-02-20T17:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T17:33:51.000Z","uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ed9104d1ec00de4f5c782b6c244d492334fce4d","tid":128353,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:33:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170220/bkncn-20170220170431403-0220_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170220%2Fbkncn-20170220170431403-0220_05011_001.html&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0OywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=0e3a46b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170220/bkncn-20170220170431403-0220_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170220/photo/bkncn-20170220170431403-0220_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170220%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170220170431403-0220_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=fa54322f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n江西上饒市玉山縣驚揭一宗自殺案，一名老翁今早做晨運時，在沿河路岸邊發現一名女子的頸部被鐵鏈勒住吊死。警方接報後立即趕赴現場調查，初步判斷其死因是自縊。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，女死者年約30歲，被發現身穿黑衣，頭部面向塔山，頸部被岸邊的鐵鏈勒住，身體垂直懸吊在半空中，警員到場後立即將她放下。玉山縣公安局表示，辦案人員初步判斷，死者是自縊而亡。目前，死者的身份未確認，案件仍在進一步調查。"}]}